channel.description:
[b][size=36pt][font=comic sans ms]Well, With the new release of Dungeoneering there have been many attempts at a successful dungeoneering cc... [/font][/size][/b] I'm starting a f2p cc just because i don't think you should have to pay money to get into a clan.

If you are interested in getting a rank in this cc, please comment so I know I should go on.
